üìò WORDPRESS FTP ERROR FIX (XAMPP LINUX)
Site Folder: golden-buyz
------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 1 ‚Äî Set Correct Owner (XAMPP user = daemon)
sudo chown -R daemon:daemon /opt/lampp/htdocs/golden-buyz

------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 2 ‚Äî Set Correct Permissions (Safe Mode)
sudo chmod -R 775 /opt/lampp/htdocs/golden-buyz

------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 3 ‚Äî Force WordPress to use Direct File Access
Edit wp-config.php:
sudo nano /opt/lampp/htdocs/golden-buyz/wp-config.php

Add this line:
define('FS_METHOD', 'direct');

Paste it above this line:
/* That's all, stop editing! Happy publishing. */

Save:
CTRL + O ‚Üí Enter
CTRL + X

------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 4 ‚Äî Restart XAMPP
sudo /opt/lampp/lampp restart

------------------------------------------------------------

üöÄ Now try installing any plugin.
‚úî FTP popup will be gone.
‚úî Plugins/Themes install without FTP.

------------------------------------------------------------

‚ö†Ô∏è FINAL HARD FIX (ONLY if still not working)
sudo chmod -R 777 /opt/lampp/htdocs/golden-buyz

(Use only on localhost; never use 777 on live servers.)
